channel.title: New Server - Need a Team
channel.description:
Hi,
I am looking to start a server up and am looking for a team to help me out.
Basically, I have a website/name already come up with. It is a .com website too. I'm looking for active and motivated people to help me out on this. I am active a lot throughout the day and also have Skype on my phone to communicate with.
What I can offer: A .com website with a name already picked out A little coding experience Activity and Motivation towards the project
What am I looking for in a Team: Motivation and Activity Creativity Professional Attitude
If you'd like to talk about joining my team, add me on skype - Garrett3650
